body.description: Express your aura with this sleek Glade PlugIns Scented Oil Air Freshener with MaxControl Technology in Empower Mint. Refresh your outlook and revive your spirit when you use Limited Edition Empower Mint fragrance oils made without phthalates, parabens, formaldehyde or nitro musks. Enrich your space with aromas of chilled mint and basil for a totally new, carefully blended minty fragrance. An easy-to-use dial control allows you to set your personalized air freshener to fit the room* or your unique aroma preference. Glade PlugIns oil warmers can express your aura in any room of your home. *Up to 550 sq. ft.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Brighter with berries
reviews.reviewText: This air freshener refills were a welcome addition today.Not quite ready to unpack but it will not be long before they’re in position.They’re so good and don’t have any issues with harming pets or anything like that. That’s a plus!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Long lasting melon scented freshener!
reviews.reviewText: These air fresheners are the refills for the Glade PlugIns. It is called wonder melon, and that describes it perfectly! It's the most clean crisp smell of watermelon but with a twist of cucumber. It's absolutely mouth watering!I love the glade refills because they cover a good bit of area and last longer. This 5 pack will fill most rooms of every home. I plan to order more once these start running low!They're easy to snap in, you literally just pop them out of the package, un screw the protective top and snap it in to your glade plug.I highly recommend these refills! They're longer lasting, great quality refills that will make any home smell great. I get so many compliments when people first walk in!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great long lasting scent
reviews.reviewText: My husband got me a scent plug in for an early Valentine's Day gift and I got these to go in them, but they don't fit the one he got me. I ended up having to use these at my office where I have a Glade one. I would make sure that your plug in is the correct brand before getting these. The post part that goes into the warmer is much longer on these than some others require. The scent itself is light and pleasing and lasts a long time. Since my office is near the restrooms, it's important for me to have something in there that smells really good and these definitely get the job done.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Wish I could adjust the scent to be even less strong
reviews.reviewText: At first sniff, I liked this scent. I always keep our plug ins on the lowest setting, but after being exposed to it for awhile, I started to find this scent to be irritating. I'll probably give the rest of these away and go back to one of our old, tried-but-true scents.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Light floral scent
reviews.reviewText: With this pack of Glade Plugin refills you get 5 .67 fl oz refills. The refills can be used with any Glade Plugin warmer. In my case I already owned a couple Glade max control plug in warmer that I could use the refills with. The refills fit the warmer perfectly and I had no issues with leakage. This is my first time trying out the Super Bloom scent and I love how light the floral scent is. I definitely recommend trying this scent if you’re looking for a more light fresh floral scent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The mango scent's a winner
reviews.reviewText: "Mighty Mango" is definitely a 'mighty' scent, stronger than most of the other Glade Plugin scents I've tried thus far and definitely realistic smelling; it's like I just stuck my nose into a freshly-cut mango. I usually prefer Air Wick for its lower price and newer warmers, but this one's a winner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Plug it in, plug it in
reviews.reviewText: Ahhhh, this plug in Glade brings back memories when I was a child and the commercial comes on. "Plug it in , plug it in". A household staple for sure. Can't live with odor or musty smell. The scent does a good job of overpowering any lingering smell.
